articles.title: ‘Stunned’ Jofra Archer left speechless after learning of Harry Brook World Cup omission live on air - Wisden
articles.description: Jofra Archer was left speechless after learning that England had left Harry Brook out of their provisional 2023 World Cup squad live on-air.
